INSERT INTO `phpbb_privmsgs_text` VALUES (3818,'567213d7e3','Yeah Yeah Yeah...  Brandon is a forgetful slack ass!  Thats twice in the last month or so he has done that.  I thought I would teach him a lesson and not  call him to see how much shit he talked.  It worked!  I know I need to get up there.  I have no idea when that time will be.  I was going to try to figure out a time to go up for a brew session when you were there, but you seem to have fallen out of the brew scene at that particular time.\r\n\r\nI made my first starters with my new stir plates!  Freakin awesome.  I plan to brew 10 gallons on Saturday.  It will be a lawnmower type beer with Vanguard hops.  If I feel froggy I may add some of whatever else is in the freezer to the beer.  I am thinking of getting a grain mill.  If I decide to do so I would have a reason to get to Cola so I can pick up some grain and those bottles!  I guess I need to have a brew shed built because I am running out of room on the front porch.  LOL  Maybe I could ask my dad to move out so I can turn the house into a brewery; what do you think?  \r\n\r\nYeah the HOD was contaminated or something.  I am not sure, but I figured out the source of that particular problem.  When I made the HOD and Cheeky Bastard; I was not doing full boils.  Since then I started doing full boils and it made a world of difference from the HOD and CB to X-1 and the IRA.  My Belgium (DT clone) is actually pretty damn close to a bottle Delirium Tremens (1st All-grain).  Don\'t worry I got you some saved of that too.\r\n\r\nWent on an interview last week with IRIX Pharmacueticals.  It went well.  Won\'t hear anything for another 2 weeks though.  I may just give up job searches and become complacent with where I am now. \r\n\r\nSo you going to be sitting in line at 12am waiting on stinking HALO 3.  I remember doing that with Brandon and damn it was COLD!  I know you have pre-ordered, but I have one question for you.  Why wait till next Thursday and Friday to geek out, when you could have Wednesday, Thursday, and Friday to geek out and jack off! \r\n\r\nAlright man, I\'m out.  Remember one thing...\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nHALO SUX and so do you!');
