INSERT INTO `phpbb_privmsgs_text` VALUES (2946,'b4661c96c6','Carl,\r\n\r\nI am not a big fan of Zorbas.  I do not like the food and the beer is so so, however, the private has been good for the club.\r\n\r\nSeveral years ago, we approached Carolina Wings (the parent company of CW\'s) on Gervais Street about using its private room as a meeting site.   The owner of the company turned us down because he was concerned about the legality of the homebrew in the restaurant.  Candidly, he probably is right.   It probably is illegal to have homebrew in a licensed restaurant.\r\n\r\nAnyway, my point is the current manager of CW\'s may be overruled by top management if we try to relocate to the Tap Room.  At Zorbas, we deal with the owners.   We operate in a legal gray area.\r\n\r\nAlso, with the large selection of beer at the Tap Room, the club meetings will become more unruly and unproductive due to increased beer consumption.\r\n\r\nIt is a tough call.   I know people want to change but I do not think it is in the best interest of the club to change to CW\'s.\r\n\r\nGerald');
