INSERT INTO `phpbb_privmsgs_text` VALUES (4753,'e8f1238d32','Here\'s the newsletter:\r\n\r\nVP of Education &amp; Recruitment\r\n\r\n Wort chilling Why do I need to do it and how do I best accomplish it? Every brewer ponders these questions at some stage of the game. Eventually almost everyone will buy a chiller of some form or another and think, Why didnt I buy one sooner? Its one of the most basic pieces of equipment and also one of the most important. The spectrum ranges from immersing the brew pot in ice water to a convoluted counter-flow chiller to a Therminator aided by a continuous whirlpool. Whats best you might ask? To answer that question our very own Barry Ledford will share some of his experiences with a multitude of methods, culminating with what he and many others believe to be the most effective and efficient method available to the homebrewer today. \r\n As many of you are aware we are facing and/or in the midst of a hop shortage. Substitutions need to be discussed. With that in mind, this is a call/plea for a member to take the educational reins at the March meeting and research the matter and share their findings for the benefit of all. Please post on the forum if youre interested in this task. \r\n Keeping spreading the gospel of PSB!');
