INSERT INTO `phpbb_privmsgs_text` VALUES (4536,'070b1d15b8','I wondered if you\'d notice the peels hardening.  I find that the most amazing.  Nice combination with the lemon and orange.  I\'ve tried to suck the everclear out of a piece of pineapple before...BIG mistake.   :cry: \r\n\r\nI\'d give it try on the 22nd.  Giada on foodnetwork only steeps hers 3 days.  I think she\'s nuts (beautiful though).  The everclear is pretty strong so it may leach out enough flavor.   *) \r\n\r\nI prefer the clear version, although in the cooler weather the creamy works well.  Instead of all milk, use 1 can of sweetened condensed milk and the remainder being milk to fill your bottle.  Several cautionary statements doing this method.  Do NOT overheat the milk as it WILL burn.  Be sure the milk is cooled completely before mixing with the everclear otherwise it breaks up and somewhat curdles.  Also I use the empty everclear bottle to measure how much to add back and have found cutting back on the non-alcoholic fluid volume helps, especially with the milk to prevent it from freezing.  Give me a call Saturday, if I have time maybe I can swing by and help.  Catch me in the mash out period.  I plan on brewing a Hen\'s Tooth clone.');
